Patuloy na napapabayaan ang kapakanan ng bawat Pilipino sa kada estado ng buhay. Korapsyon at Kakulangan ng Alaga at Pansin ay patuloy pa rin nangyayari kahit sino pang umupo sa pwestong kataas-taasan. 

𝙏𝙖𝙢𝙖 𝙣𝙖 𝙖𝙣𝙜 𝙥𝙖𝙜𝙨𝙖𝙨𝙖𝙢𝙖𝙣𝙩𝙖𝙡𝙖 — 𝙥𝙖𝙣𝙖𝙜𝙪𝙩𝙞𝙣 𝙖𝙣𝙜 𝙙𝙖𝙥𝙖𝙩 𝙢𝙖𝙣𝙖𝙜𝙤𝙩.

Caption by Jesthin Bhenuald Maniago 
Publication Material by Cheska Tobias

message.text:
𝐇𝐨𝐫𝐧𝐬 𝐔𝐩, 𝐏𝐀𝐓𝐀𝐦𝐬!

It's that time of the year again! Be ready to put your game faces on as the 𝗜𝗧𝗛𝗠 𝗦𝗽𝗼𝗿𝘁𝘀𝗳𝗲𝘀𝘁 𝘁𝗿𝘆-𝗼𝘂𝘁𝘀 are bound to begin! Whether you're a returning athlete or trying something new, this is your chance to rise, represent, and showcase your grit in this year's most anticipated event!

🗓️: 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟮𝟬, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱 (𝗦𝗮𝘁𝘂𝗿𝗱𝗮𝘆)
⏰: 𝟲:𝟯𝟬 𝗣𝗠 - 𝟴:𝟯𝟬 𝗣𝗠
📍: 𝗙𝗘𝗨 𝗖𝗼𝘂𝗿𝘁

Now is the time to show us what you've got! Push your limits, rise to the challenge and earn your spot, PATAms! 

Caption by: Jea Madronio
Pubmat by: Vince Maligang

📍: 𝗙𝗘𝗨 𝗖𝗼𝘂𝗿𝘁

Now is the time to show us what you've got! Push your limits, rise to the challenge and earn your spot, PATAms! 

Caption by: Jea Madronio
Pubmat by: Vince Maligang

#PATAPHFEU

𝐇𝐨𝐫𝐧𝐬 𝐔𝐩, 𝐏𝐀𝐓𝐀𝐦𝐬!

It's that time of the year again! Be ready to put your game faces on as the 𝗜𝗧𝗛𝗠 𝗦𝗽𝗼𝗿𝘁𝘀𝗳𝗲𝘀𝘁 𝘁𝗿𝘆-𝗼𝘂𝘁𝘀 are bound to begin! Whether you're a returning athlete or trying something new, this is your chance to rise, represent, and showcase your grit in this year's most anticipated event!

🗓️: 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟮𝟬, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱 (𝗦𝗮𝘁𝘂𝗿𝗱𝗮𝘆)
⏰: 𝟲:𝟯𝟬 𝗣𝗠 - 𝟴:𝟯𝟬 𝗣𝗠
📍: 𝗙𝗘𝗨 𝗖𝗼𝘂𝗿𝘁

Now is the time to show us what you've got! Push your limits, rise to the challenge and earn your spot, PATAms! 

Caption by: Jea Madronio
Pubmat by: Vince Maligang

#PATAPHFEU
